&lt;p>腳本連結：&lt;a href="https://github.com/880831ian/aws-ssm-ec2-rds-elasticacahe-msk-scp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/880831ian/aws-ssm-ec2-rds-elasticacahe-msk-scp&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;br>
&lt;figure>&lt;img src="https://pin-yi.me/aws/aws-ssm-ec2-rds-elasticacahe-msk-scp/1.webp"
alt="腳本使用" width="450">&lt;figcaption>
&lt;p>腳本使用&lt;/p>
&lt;/figcaption>
